    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Break the cycle through knowledge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Almear is a turn-based narrative RPG set in a time loop. Players embody a character who endlessly relives the same day, carrying their memories from one cycle to the next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/58959a43eda09a9cd4ac9842ee534a3e.poster.avif?t=1771167618\" width=450 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/58959a43eda09a9cd4ac9842ee534a3e.webm?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/58959a43eda09a9cd4ac9842ee534a3e.mp4?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knowledge is your progression:</strong> Progression doesn't rely on power or gear, but on accumulated information. Discover what characters know, what they hide, and what they forget after each reset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/c653807df1c94c51588f4dc25a698cc8.poster.avif?t=1771167618\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/c653807df1c94c51588f4dc25a698cc8.webm?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/c653807df1c94c51588f4dc25a698cc8.mp4?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Impactful choices:</strong> Gathered information unlocks new options in future loops: avoid combat, access unique dialogues, or trigger radically different consequences. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Persistent characters:</strong> Some characters maintain a form of continuity across loops, influencing their behavior and role over time. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A strategic and calm approach:</strong> Often, understanding the world and its inhabitants is more important than overcoming them by force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/a1c0a703571826f3b510f38d3b6d1272.poster.avif?t=1771167618\" width=450 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/a1c0a703571826f3b510f38d3b6d1272.webm?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/a1c0a703571826f3b510f38d3b6d1272.mp4?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/529a8660c1604921207a8d0559c7d147.poster.avif?t=1771167618\" width=450 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/529a8660c1604921207a8d0559c7d147.webm?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316400/extras/529a8660c1604921207a8d0559c7d147.mp4?t=1771167618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul>",
